{"word":"H2131 - זִיקָה - zîyqâh - zee-kaw' - Chain","slug":"H2131","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">זִיקָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>zîyqâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>zee-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D6;&#x05E7;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D6;&#x05E7;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D6;&#x05D9;&#x05E7;&#x05D4; - z&#x0131;&#x0302;yqa&#x0302;h  ziq  ze&#x0302;q</b> - <i>zee-kaw', zeek, zake</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2187\">H2187</a>; properly what <i>leaps</i> forth, that is, <i>flash</i> of fire, or a burning <i>arrow</i>; also (from the original sense of the root) a <i>bond: - </i>chain, fetter, firebrand, spark."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H246\">H246</a>"}]}